Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.03,0:00:06.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That child said he wanted to see the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:09.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I couldn't take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:12.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There were so many things I wanted to do for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.71,0:00:15.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I couldn't do a single thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:19.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even though the summer had just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:40.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:43.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:49.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:50.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:28.67,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:41.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad Kirishima-san recovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:48.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, when I saw that feather, I also had a kinda mysterious feeling.
Comment: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:50.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: I felt strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:53.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:56.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been spaced out ever since you got up.
Comment: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:56.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: woke up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:56.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:59.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream of when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:00.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:02.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to worry about.
Comment: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:02.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:05.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, are you still having those dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:07.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:12.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night's dream was different from anything I've had before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:15.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon was out and it was so bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:18.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to fly up to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:22.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sore all over, but I kept trying to go higher and higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:25.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I heard voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:25.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Voices?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:30.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The voices of many people, trying to restrain me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:35.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They echoed in my ears, so I couldn't climb anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:38.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:38.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:41.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:42.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, be carefu-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:45.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah!
Comment: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:45.95,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,LUNA'S BAR
Comment: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:45.95,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Asahi
Comment: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:45.95,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Used Book Store
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:55.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:55.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great, isn't it, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:59.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how it's walking without any strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:03.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:05.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It got up! It got up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:08.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the way kids should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.04,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:10.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shouldn't you be with Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:10.21,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko?
Comment: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:10.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: by Kano's side
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:13.92,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:13.92,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko piko pikori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:16.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she went to school to take care of the animals today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:20.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why am I talking to you like it's normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:23.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:27.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doll-san, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shake hands, shake hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:32.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:36.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:39.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what being "really close" is like, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:40.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't make any money again.
Comment: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:49.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: I worked for free again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:52.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That Misuzu is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:56.53,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Munch munch munch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:58.49,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Chew chew chew chew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:04:59.76,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mumchy munchy munchy munchy munchy munchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:02.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:02.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:05.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:05.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:06.64,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:07.60,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa hah hoo hooey hee?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:09.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to say something, swallow first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:13.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:15.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:17.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Misuzu?
Comment: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:17.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Did misuzu come this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamio-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:20.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:21.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:25.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:25.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you make hamburgers tomorrow too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:25.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:25.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a little pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:36.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:39.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You let go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:06:05.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:05.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:05.16,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:07.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to use the shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:12.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:12.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get the keys to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:17.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was the stationmaster here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:20.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's not working here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:23.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he working somewhere else?
Comment: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Did he find a different job?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:28.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:28.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a token of apology, here.
Comment: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:31.18,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,RICE COUPON
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:31.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:35.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:38.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the bottle I found yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:41.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is startdust,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:46.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,sand grains shaped like baby stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:48.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, is it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:49.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:52.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They rustle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:57.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-san too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:57.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can have one too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:04.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, the three of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:06.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:15.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This sand was given to me by my father, when I was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:18.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then isn't it something precious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Comment: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:19.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Is it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:23.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if it's Kunisaki-san and Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:30.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Kamio-san has already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:31.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:36.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible she stayed at school this late?
Comment: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:36.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Awkward phrashing maybe above?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:42.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kunisaki-san, are you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:48.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:52.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:52.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars are already out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the other club members?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:59.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the only member.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:00.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:03.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm club president.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a really selective club.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:06.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:20.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. This is the first time I've brought her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:27.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:27.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you're not going out of your way to be here, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:30.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:37.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted the three of us to observe the stars together,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:41.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because she seems to like you, Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:51.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:51.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She talks about you constantly when she is with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:55.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She really likes you, Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell how she feels,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:03.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because she is my other half.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Other half?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:13.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru and I have always spent our time together, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:20.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:20.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-san, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:23.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:27.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,... always traveling alone, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:31.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever spent time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:36.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The happiness of spending time with someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:40.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The joy of living for someone else's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:46.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even someone like me should have done,
Comment: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:46.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Done unnecessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,though it was a long, long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:52.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:52.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:54.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:56.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then it's Michiru Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:57.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:01.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to walk me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:04.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:04.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not like tall girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:12.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:12.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A good figure is an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:13.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:18.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I happen to be rather proud of it myself too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:19.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Happen to be rather, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Happen to be.
Comment: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:21.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Super awkward. Needs rephrasing I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:27.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The taller you are, the closer you are to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:31.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for walking me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful walking home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:37.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:38.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:41.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, who are you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:43.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A new member of the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:45.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:48.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:51.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:51.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:55.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:55.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I helped her with some heavy bags the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:11:00.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for having you go to the trouble of walking my daughter home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come on inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:02.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:10.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:12.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner is already ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:15.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tohno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:16.07,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:26.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Comment: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.55,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm\Ndoing my\Nhomework.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:38.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:45.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:48.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:49.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:52.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukito-san, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:54.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still night now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:58.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have told me you had to stay late at supplemental classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:01.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:01.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:04.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:08.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you keeping a picture diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:12.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my choice of assignment for the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:14.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maestro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:14.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you betray me?!
Comment: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:17.13,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids! Please watch this show in a bright room,
Comment: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:18.47,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,And make sure to sit far from the TV!
Comment: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.13,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Unedited Typesetting. I think not to include it tbh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:17.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:19.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can conduct this orchestra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:22.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:26.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't conduct, who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:27.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give the baton to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:30.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way you'll get it is over my dead body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:37.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Appassionato God Fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geh! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:41.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the best part!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:46.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:53.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to play cards with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:56.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:12:58.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:58.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:09.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:09.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Old Maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:09.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Poker?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:13.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it something simple that doesn't require thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:16.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, let's play Concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:25.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:27.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:28.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:31.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:35.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:47.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:52.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can play.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try my hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:58.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try my hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:13:58.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:01.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:01.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:04.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:11.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:11.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:11.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:14.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself!
Comment: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:15.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:18.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu suddenlyâ€“
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:22.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind stepping outside for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:24.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:40.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:44.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been like this ever since she was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:48.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She becomes like that, right when she's about to make a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right when she's about to make a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:55.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had the doctor at the clinic look at her, and I've even tried going to a big hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:57.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:15:02.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They all said it was probably only psychological and she'd grow out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:06.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She actually had an episode at school today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:08.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They called me at work, so I went to pick her up on my bike,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:12.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and brought her straight home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:15.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:20.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was expecting and hoping that she'd be all right with you,
Comment: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:21.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Awkard phrase above.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:24.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,since she's all right when she's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:39.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll suffer these attacks as long as I'm here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:41.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should keep my distance for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:49.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her that I'll still keep walking her to and from school, just like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over for dinner every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:06.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault that you weren't able to stay at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:08.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you lonely living by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:13.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm living alone, I've made quite a few friends somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:16.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have some friends too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:16.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:19.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:25.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because whenever I'm about to make a friend, I start crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:26.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone always runs away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:29.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have Haruko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:29.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:33.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not my real mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:36.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:40.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko-san is actually my aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:43.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was dumped onto her because I was such a strange kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:49.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko-san didn't want me, but in the end, I had to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I don't want to cause her trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:56.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we live our separate lives under one roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:03.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a real burden on her, and I don't want to be any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:09.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I play by myself, looking for weird juices, or playing cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:13.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:17.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:21.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:25.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:34.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi hasn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:37.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's at school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:37.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be here soon.
Comment: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:37.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,alt: eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:40.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not supposed to be at school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:54.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:56.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:17:59.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:17:59.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:03.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:03.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an indirect kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:03.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about adult stuff!
Comment: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:07.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,awkard phrasing maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:09.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:19.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:23.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:24.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bubbles are so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:29.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're empty, just like the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:32.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:34.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:41.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try going to her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:44.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she isn't coming, then we should go visit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:50.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:53.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go to her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:56.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're her friend, right?
Comment: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:56.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: You're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:57.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never been?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:19:02.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:03.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to pick up Misuzu too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:03.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for walking me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I can't stay today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:10.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not eating dinner with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:13.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have somewhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:20.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:20.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:25.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I met you yesterday, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:25.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the new member of the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:29.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm running an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:29.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May I see your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:31.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has she gone somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:35.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:38.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you've got the right address?
Comment: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:38.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: address -> house
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:39.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:39.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me, right?
Comment: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:41.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: You're joking
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:41.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:45.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, skipping work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:50.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohno-san's mother has been suffering a psychological disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:54.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been checking on her every time I get a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:59.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She convinced herself that her elder daughter, Minagi-san, is her younger daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:19:59.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the one who passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:02.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She believed that for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:05.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems her condition has suddenly changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:09.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When she accepted the fact that her younger daughter was dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:11.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she erased Minagi-san from her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:17.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In her mind, neither one of her daughters ever existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:33.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to have a little sister, named Michiru,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:36.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a precious little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:43.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother was sad because I was close to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:48.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The baby she was expecting was supposed to fill the hole in her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:54.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could have just one dream come true, what would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:57.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:20:59.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:07.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother couldn't accept the reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:07.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so she chose to live in her dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:11.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I became a fragment of that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:17.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But last night, she saw herself in a dream having a miscarriage of Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:22.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Kirishima-sensei, that made my mother accept the reality.
Comment: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:24.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: My mother accepted the reality after seeing that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:30.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, when she saw me, my mother said,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:32.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Who are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:34.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:38.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:44.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the end of my dream, in which I lived as Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.37,0:21:51.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My wings have forgotten how to fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:58.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because I always just pretended to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:03.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a use for wings that cannot fly?
Comment: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:40.38,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.38,0:23:42.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.62,0:23:42.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're more suited to travel than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.22,0:23:48.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come with me, Tohno?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.81,0:23:49.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:52.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something has to change.
Comment: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:51.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: It's not good being like this after all. Context: Minagi has to wake up from her dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:24:01.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to show you the world;
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.16,0:24:03.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the real world, not a dream world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.57,0:24:07.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything started with my sin...
Comment: 0,0:24:07.74,0:24:10.14,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 6